## Context

Transformers.js supports numerous pipelines but lacks a generic pipeline for modern visual language models (VLMs) like SmolVLM, LLaVA, Qwen2-VL, and PaliGemma, which accept both an image and a text prompt and generate text. The underlying model class `AutoModelForImageTextToText` already exists in `src/models.js` (line 8736) and maps 11 model architectures (llava, smolvlm, qwen2-vl, paligemma, etc.). This plan adds the `image-text-to-text` pipeline to wire it all together.

